fields.title: Cricket makes a friend
fields.content: Cricket made a new friend at daycare today.

fields.title: Squid finds a good pillow
fields.content: Squid found a very comfy fluffy pillow. It wriggled a bit though....

fields.title: Cricket & Sushi finally have a hug
fields.content: After a few weeks of being unsure of the newest family member, Cricket finally decides that Sushi is pretty great and they hug it out.

fields.title: Sushi has a sleep
fields.content: Sushi loves her round snuggle bed. You can always find her hanging out in it. If she isn't sleeping she's making great biscuits!
